t’s already on the battlefield.£7/1/2012: You can choose not to copy anything. In that case, Clone enters the battlefield as a 0/0 Shapeshifter creature, and is probably put into the graveyard immediately.£7/1/2013: Clone’s ability doesn’t target the chosen creature.','U',NULL,'0.19','0.44','1.9',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'U',NULL,NULL,'Clone','Klon','Clone',NULL,'Clone',NULL,'Clon',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Créature : Clone','Kreatur — Klon','Creatura — Clone',NULL,'Criatura — Clone',NULL,'Criatura — Clon',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Au moment où le Clone arrive en jeu, vous pouvez choisir une créature en jeu. Si vous faites ainsi, le Clone arrive en jeu comme une copie de cette créature.','Sowie der Klon ins Spiel kommt, kannst du eine Kreatur im Spiel bestimmen. Falls du dies tust, kommt der Klon als eine Kopie dieser Kreatur ins Spiel.','Mentre il Clone entra in gioco, puoi scegliere una creatura in gioco. Se lo fai, il Clone entra in gioco come una copia di quella creatura.',NULL,'Conforme Clone entra em jogo, você pode escolher uma criatura em jogo. Se o fizer, Clone entra em jogo como uma cópia daquela criatura.',NULL,'En cuanto el Clon entre en juego, puedes elegir una criatura en juego. Si lo haces, el Clon entra en juego como una copia de esa criatura.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('34397','Commando Raid','ON','Instant','U','{2}{R}','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Until end of turn, target creature you control gains "When this creature deals combat damage to a player, you may have it deal damage equal to its power to target creature that player controls."',NULL,NULL,'Ron Spencer','195','2.875',NULL,'R',NULL,'0.03','0.22','0.95',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'R',NULL,NULL,'Raid commando','Kommandoüberfall','Raid del Commando',NULL,'Investida de Comandos',NULL,'Incursión de comando',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Éphémère','Spontanzauber','Istantaneo',NULL,'Mágica Instantânea',NULL,'Instantáneo',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Jusqu''à la fin du tour