iggered abilities from cycling a card and the cycling ability itself aren’t spells. Effects that interact with spells (such as that of Cancel) won’t affect them.£4/18/2017: You can cycle a card even if it has a triggered ability from cycling that won’t have a legal target. This is because the cycling ability and the triggered ability are separate. This also means that if either ability doesn’t resolve (due to being countered with Disallow, for example, or if the triggered ability’s targets have become illegal), the other ability will still resolve.£1/19/2018: There are many important moments in the story, but the most crucial—called “story spotlights”—are shown on cards. These cards have the Planeswalker symbol in their text box; this symbol has no effect on gameplay. You can read more about these events in the official Magic fiction at http://www.mtgstory.com.','W',NULL,'0.05','0.19','0.94',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'W',NULL,NULL,'Foi renouvelée','Bestärkter Glauben','Fede Rinnovata',NULL,'Fé Renovada',NULL,'Fe renovada',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Éphémère','Spontanzauber','Istantaneo',NULL,'Mágica Instantânea',NULL,'Instantáneo',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Vous gagnez 6 points de vie.£Recyclage {1}{W} #_({1}{W}, défaussez-vous de cette carte de votre main : Piochez une carte.)_#£Quand vous recyclez la Foi renouvelée, vous pouvez gagner 2 points de vie.','Du erhältst 6 Lebenspunkte dazu.£Umwandlung {1}{W} #_({1}{W}, wirf diese Karte aus deiner Hand ab: Ziehe eine Karte.)_#£Wenn du den Bestärkten Glauben umwandelst, kannst du 2 Lebenspunkte dazuerhalten.','Guadagni 6 punti vita.£Ciclo {1}{W} #_({1}{W}, Scarta questa carta dalla tua mano: Pesca una carta)_#.£Quando usi l''abilità ciclo della Fede Rinnovata, puoi guadagnare 2 punti vita.',NULL,'Você ganha 6 pontos de vida.£Reciclar {1}{W} #_({1}{W}, Descarte este card de sua mão: Compre um card.)_#£Quando reciclar Fé Renovada, você pode ganhar 2 pontos de vida.',NULL,'Gana 6 vidas.£Ciclo {1}{W}. #_({1}{W}, descartar esta carta de tu mano: Roba un